<h4 class="subtext"> Suad is an entrepreneur, content creator and software developer and  with a passion for holistic wellness and digital innovation.
    On an entrepreneurship journey that began in law school as a wellness enthusiast on a quest to simplify selfcare by providing affordable yet effective African skincare products.
    Shortly after, my legal professional journey took off as a Legal Researcher at oil and gas firm Tullow Oil. 
    Embracing the digital age and answering what seemed like a natural calling I ventured into social media management as a freelancer working with an array of companies
    from events, to child education, skincare and legal tech. From there, i completed an intensive business and technology training program at 
    the Meltwater Entrepreneurial School of Technology (MEST)
     
